    <item>
      <title>乌克兰为何需要与债券持有人达成新协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/ukraine-economy-why-kyiv-needs-a-new-deal-with-its-bondholders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离乌克兰 200 亿美元债券的两年延期还款期结束仅剩几周时间，乌克兰必须恢复向私人债权人支付利息。债务重组谈判迄今未能达成协议，双方在债券持有人应牺牲多少投资的问题上争执不休。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/ukraine-economy-why-kyiv-needs-a-new-deal-with-its-bondholders</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 13:50:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
